title: The Mandarian Orange Show Episode 74- Bad Hammer Time, or: 30 Day MoviePass Challenge Part 3
description: In this episode, Phil and Janelle talk about the next movies in the 30 Day MoviePass Challenge! They also discuss Thanksgiving, Back to the Future, a really bad movie, Tom Cruise, Lyndon B Johnson, Laughlin, bad construction timing, and more.

title: Finding yourself in the character by justifying your actions
description: The best way to find authenticity in characters outside of your wheelhouse. Powerful stuff.
